{"id":1735152,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-21T12:47:19.043Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1735152,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Kerana Anisa","overview":"# Kerana Anisa  The story tells of Anisa and Syukri who are close friends in their village. Anisa has a big dream in life when she aspires to become a lawyer and asks Syukri to be her \"teacher\" and source of encouragement. However, Anisa's father, Long Yahya, opposes Syukri and Anisa's friendship. After Anisa completes her Malaysian Certificate of Education (SPM), Syukri leaves for London to continue his studies, but they maintain their relationship through letters. One day, Anisa is shocked by a marriage proposal entourage from Zahid, a wealthy man's son from her village. Zahid is attracted to Anisa's beauty and uses his parents' wealth to win over her father. Anisa opposes this because she wants to continue her studies, especially since she passed her SPM with flying colors. However, Anisa is forced to marry. After marriage, Zahid treats Anisa cruelly both physically and emotionally.","popularity":0,"poster_path":"/mL38jUHcyHozedXiIlmrn5LuU79.jpg","production_companies":[],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2016-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Kerana Anisa","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":1551059,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Zara Zya","original_name":"Zara Zya","popularity":0.5486,"profile_path":"/3w41lPTPVyBr2dGvUa49nsJCZX.jpg","cast_id":2,"character":"","credit_id":"6a5ed2d1c45ea9aeb09121c2","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1742616,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Mustaqim Bahadon","original_name":"Mustaqim Bahadon","popularity":0.2081,"profile_path":"/65T3Ws5Ik5NtM8E